---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Athletics" description="PBASA athletics program - building strong bodies, minds, and future leaders through daily movement and competitive sports.">

  <PageHero title="Athletics" subtitle="Building strong bodies, strong minds, and future leaders through sports and movement." />

  <!-- Intro with Image -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xl text-navy-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Our athletics program is designed to inspire a lifelong love for physical activity, teamwork, and personal growth. Through daily movement and sports, students build confidence, develop healthy habits, and learn the value of hard work and working together.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl text-navy-700 leading-relaxed">
            Every student participates in athletics before, during, or after school, giving each child the opportunity to stay active, improve their skills, and feel the pride of being part of a team.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <img src="/images/athletics-action.jpg" alt="Students in athletics" class="w-full h-72 object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sports Offered -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-navy-50">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-gold-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Programs</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900 mt-3 mb-6">Sports We Offer</h2>
        <div class="gold-divider mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">&#127936;</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Basketball</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">&#9971;</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Golf</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">&#127934;</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Tennis</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">&#9917;</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Soccer</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">&#127944;</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Flag Football</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">&#127939;</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Running</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 text-center shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow col-span-2 sm:col-span-1">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">&#128170;</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Coordination Games</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Grade Level Breakdown -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-gold-600 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">By Grade Level</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900 mt-3 mb-6">Athletic Development</h2>
        <div class="gold-divider mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-navy-600 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">In addition to the Florida Physical Education State Standards, our athletics program is designed to meet students where they are and grow with them.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- K-2 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gold-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gold-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gold-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">K-2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Foundation Building</h3>
              <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm">Kindergarten through 2nd Grade</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Students in K-2 develop balance, coordination, strength, and flexibility while learning healthy eating habits.
          </p>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">
            Through fun activities, they also build ball control, footwork, and hand-eye coordination, creating a strong foundation for movement and athletic development.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gold-100 text-gold-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Balance</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gold-100 text-gold-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Coordination</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gold-100 text-gold-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Strength</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gold-100 text-gold-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Flexibility</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gold-100 text-gold-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Healthy Habits</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3-8 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-50 to-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-navy-200">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">3-8</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-navy-900">Competitive Growth</h3>
              <p class="text-navy-500 text-sm">3rd through 8th Grade</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Students in 3rd-8th grade begin competing in travel sports, developing their ability to compete while improving skills such as teamwork, game strategy, footwork, ball control, speed, agility, and decision-making.
          </p>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">
            Through competition and training, students grow both physically and mentally.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-navy-100 text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Teamwork</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-navy-100 text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Game Strategy</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-navy-100 text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Speed &amp; Agility</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-navy-100 text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Decision-Making</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-navy-100 text-navy-700 text-xs font-medium rounded-full">Travel Sports</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-navy-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container-narrow max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">Give Your Child the Athletic Edge</h2>
      <p class="text-navy-200 text-lg mb-8">Every student at PBASA participates in athletics. It's part of who we are.</p>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1CuhqVLxdc6ujO8y3FLcWLoVdVuoKK6SDI2h0ay5Hulo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary text-lg">
        Pre-Enroll Today
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
